像 crud 没有什么困难，怎么回答好？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/856854","created":1654132816,"deleted":0,"content":"","content_rendered":"","last_modified":1654132816,"replies":18,"id":856854},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_large.png?m=1650127482","name":"shanghai","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_normal.png?m=1650127482","title":"上海","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/shanghai","topics":2854,"footer":"","header":"","title_alternative":"Shanghai","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_mini.png?m=1650127482","stars":2049,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":18,"parent_node_name":"cn"},"member":{"id":464696,"username":"c7in7","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/c7in7","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"网管。","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a982/297d/464696_mini.png?m=1654147900","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a982/297d/464696_normal.png?m=1654147900","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a982/297d/464696_large.png?m=1654147900","created":1578885597,"last_modified":1654147900},"last_reply_by":"kera0a","last_touched":1654151394,"title":"今晚可能要骑车回家了","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/856919","created":1654148426,"deleted":0,"content":"上海复工了，作为第一批被叫到公司的人内心本就诸多不爽。研究了一下 72h 核酸的时效，昨晚排了 2 小时的队，经历了 1 人一管到没管子，做到我的时候已经 10 人一管了，不过总算做好了。\r\n\r\n回家后感觉十分疲惫，昨天体感温度在 30 度左右，湿度 73%，直接洗漱躺着。早上 6 点被吵醒，看了一眼核酸结果依旧没出，躺到 7 点起床洗漱，上一次核酸是在 30 号的 8：17 ，只要我在 8：17 前进地铁扫码应该问题不大。\r\n\r\n下车后发现公司边上的小桃园开了，只能打包，不知道是打包费还是涨价了，多收了我 1 块钱。由于 72h 核酸已过期，没去便利店。\r\n\r\n中午了，结果依旧没出，找了一家馄饨店，没扫码直接点了一份回公司吃（商务楼发了通行证，有通行证的不用扫码）。\r\n\r\n现在是 2022 年 06 月 02 日 13:38 ，依旧没结果，看了一下回家骑车要 40 分钟，还好，可以接受。不知道是我哪管出问题了还是昨天的量太多没检测完，总之影响的不是决策者和执行者。","content_rendered":"<p>上海复工了，作为第一批被叫到公司的人内心本就诸多不爽。研究了一下 72h 核酸的时效，昨晚排了 2 小时的队，经历了 1 人一管到没管子，做到我的时候已经 10 人一管了，不过总算做好了。</p>\n<p>回家后感觉十分疲惫，昨天体感温度在 30 度左右，湿度 73%，直接洗漱躺着。早上 6 点被吵醒，看了一眼核酸结果依旧没出，躺到 7 点起床洗漱，上一次核酸是在 30 号的 8：17 ，只要我在 8：17 前进地铁扫码应该问题不大。</p>\n<p>下车后发现公司边上的小桃园开了，只能打包，不知道是打包费还是涨价了，多收了我 1 块钱。由于 72h 核酸已过期，没去便利店。</p>\n<p>中午了，结果依旧没出，找了一家馄饨店，没扫码直接点了一份回公司吃（商务楼发了通行证，有通行证的不用扫码）。</p>\n<p>现在是 2022 年 06 月 02 日 13:38 ，依旧没结果，看了一下回家骑车要 40 分钟，还好，可以接受。不知道是我哪管出问题了还是昨天的量太多没检测完，总之影响的不是决策者和执行者。</p>\n","last_modified":1654148426,"replies":17,"id":856919},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1651385949","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1651385949","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":49060,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1651385949","stars":7844,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":355958,"username":"microxiaoxiao","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/microxiaoxiao","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2b343cbcc00a1ed3d171b2aec6a5b4e5?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2b343cbcc00a1ed3d171b2aec6a5b4e5?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2b343cbcc00a1ed3d171b2aec6a5b4e5?s=73&d=retro","created":1539457745,"last_modified":1653922165},"last_reply_by":"Buges","last_touched":1654146769,"title":"最近用 C++实现了一个库，上层应用是 Java ，听 BA 说，如果 Java 通过 JNI 调用 C++会存在不稳定的情况，是真的嘛？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/856885","created":1654139508,"deleted":0,"content":"","content_rendered":"","last_modified":1654139508,"replies":16,"id":856885},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":185509,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3488,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":326377,"username":"tojohnonly","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/tojohnonly","website":"https://tojohnonly.github.io/","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"Shenzhen","tagline":"trip to Ensk...","bio":"你说你孤独，就像长星照耀十三个州府…","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a553/f4a7/326377_mini.png?m=1638929503","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a553/f4a7/326377_normal.png?m=1638929503","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a553/f4a7/326377_large.png?m=1638929503","created":1530538105,"last_modified":1638929503},"last_reply_by":"shadowVincent","last_touched":1654143917,"title":"游戏本怎么优雅的立起来当主机使用","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/856882","created":1654138266,"deleted":0,"content":"笔记本是去年买的 Y9000P ，在宿舍一直是连接显示器当主机使用，偶尔出去或者回老家才当笔记本用。\r\n\r\n问题是，当主机使用，总是要半开盖子，放在旁边，有点占用地方。在不拆机修改开关机跳线的前提下，不能像 Macbook 那样直接直接立着节省空间。搜的支架要么是平着的，要么是立着的。\r\n\r\n有没有那种支持半开的立式支架，或者更优雅的当主机的方式？","content_rendered":"<p>笔记本是去年买的 Y9000P ，在宿舍一直是连接显示器当主机使用，偶尔出去或者回老家才当笔记本用。</p>\n<p>问题是，当主机使用，总是要半开盖子，放在旁边，有点占用地方。在不拆机修改开关机跳线的前提下，不能像 Macbook 那样直接直接立着节省空间。搜的支架要么是平着的，要么是立着的。</p>\n<p>有没有那种支持半开的立式支架，或者更优雅的当主机的方式？</p>\n","last_modified":1654138266,"replies":16,"id":856882},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1650127281","name":"share","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1650127281","title":"分享发现","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","topics":35561,"footer":"","header":"分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。","title_alternative":"Share","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","stars":4847,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":16,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":168219,"username":"Steps","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Steps","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"http