"last_touched":1654149300,"title":"Python if 语句写法，能更精简更难懂吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/856888","created":1654140086,"deleted":0,"content":"正常写法：\r\n\r\n```\r\nif a == 1:\r\n    x = 1\r\n    y = 2\r\nelif a in [2, 3] and b == 1:\r\n    x = 1\r\n    y = 3\r\n```\r\n\r\n少几行代码，可读性变差：\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\nif a == 1 or (a in [2, 3] and b == 1):\r\n    x = 1\r\n    y = 2 if a == 1 else 3\r\n```\r\n\r\n还有其他写法吗？","content_rendered":"<p>正常写法：</p>\n<pre><code>if a == 1:\n    x = 1\n    y = 2\nelif a in [2, 3] and b == 1:\n    x = 1\n    y = 3\n</code></pre>\n<p>少几行代码，可读性变差：</p>\n<pre><code>if a == 1 or (a in [2, 3] and b == 1):\n    x = 1\n    y = 2 if a == 1 else 3\n</code></pre>\n<p>还有其他写法吗？</p>\n","last_modified":1654140086,"replies":12,"id":856888}]